Result.Title: London in 24hrs
Result.Summary: As the first stop in our 2 week whirlwind tour of Europe, London didn't fail to impress. My last visit to London was even shorter, a mere few hours spent in the hotel before waking up early in the morning to catch a flight back to the states. This time, the length of stay has at least been doubled -- which is not saying much, but definitely headed in the right direction. Climbing out of the St. Paul tube station, we had no trouble finding our hotel -- Club Quarters St. Paul's , which is just 50 feet away from the grand cathedral and exactly where Google map showed it to be.
